                        ‡∏ß‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏ô
                    </label>
                    <input type="date" x-model="startDate" class="w-full border rounded px-3 py-2">
                </div>
